Hanson Trust Plc &lt;HAN> said its U.S.subsidiary, Hanson Industries, sold PCR Inc, a specialtychemicals unit, for 6.25 mln dlrs in cash to &lt;Chemical PartnersInc>.    Hanson Industries said it acquired PCR Inc in 1986 as partof its purchase of &lt;SCM Corp>.    PCR Inc posted an operating loss in 1986 of 381,000 dlrs onsales of 13.2 mln dlrs, the company said. Reuter&#3;